<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-03-06T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-03-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="1366" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1366">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 412.11/59.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">American
                                    Ambassador</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">No. 750.]</seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-03-06">
                                    <hi rend="italic">March 6, 1912</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: The Department has received your No. 1266
                            of the 19th ultimo, containing the substance of your interview on the
                            15th [etc.].</p>
                        <p>You will continue to keep this matter prominently before the eyes of the
                            Mexican Government and to impress them on all appropriate occasions with
                            the necessity of making a liberal and early adjustment of all these
                            claims.</p>
                        <p>I am [etc.]</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Huntington Wilson.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>